rows.label: qev027004_MSG0001
rows.name: Welcome back. And and and nice work, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0002
rows.name:
I hear you gave the big jerk who shot me a real
walloping, didn't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0003
rows.name:
Many many thanks. Now I can finally sleep at night,
can't I?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0004
rows.name:
Not to mention climbing up on the roof to work, yes?
Or even dancing around for no reason?
I can go all day now if I want![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0005
rows.name:
My days of fearing Ganglion attacks while doing
maintenance are over, aren't they?
My productivity's going to skyrocket now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0006
rows.name:
You're a literal lifesaver, aren't you?
So so so many thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0007
rows.name:
And even aside from that, you seem like the type I'd be
happy to call a friend, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0008
rows.name:
Yeah! We're more than just savior and savior-ee, no?
At this point, we're buddies![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0009
rows.name:
Feel free to come by and hang out anytime, okay?
No awkward hero worship, I promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev027004_MSG0010
rows.name: We'll be be be waiting for you![ST:wait ]
